data.description: FABULOUS REMODELED RANCH STRAIGHT OUT OF BETTER HOMES & GARDENS!!! Welcome to 4602 Fox Chase Dr..  This STUNNING 3 bedroom 2 bath home w/ approx 2,211 sq, ft is situated on approx. 1 acre w/ an attached 2 c side entry garage & GINORMOUS detached garage that can accommodate up to 6 cars if needed, there is electric/ water/furnace/A/C & 1/2 bath... Currently part of the garage is being used as a Man Cave... There are also 2 separate carports attached.. Sellers have done a impressive remodel over the past few years. Enter into the ALL OPEN FLOOR PLAN w/ hardwood flooring / unique compass inlay as well. The entry features a wall of wainscoting, The family room features a  fireplace (gas or wood) with unique built in book shelves on each side. The bay window brings in so much natural light. Beautiful kitchen with built in stove & cooktop w/ bar. Nice size open dining room will accommodate large furniture. There is a  cozy den located off dining & family room. If that's not enough there is a charming large screened in porch, approx. 12 x 25 that you will love to spend your evenings relaxing. The primary bedroom is so cozy, enjoy these cold winter nights falling asleep by the electric built in fireplace located on a decorator wall with shiplap. You will love the walk in closet, plenty of shelving & hanging area (the 2 grey shelves not attached will not remain) The primary bath has a pretty updated vanity, stand up shower & walk in closet. The hall bathroom was completely remodeled with decorator vanity. 2 more adorable bedrooms complete this ranch. The flat 1-acre lot has a covered patio area w/ large Koi Pond (please read more info in documents). The backyard is partially fenced. This home won't last long!!! Located in Fox Chase Subdivision only minutes to I 65 & Gene Snyder.
